  "title": "Legal Secretary [Corporate]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Training & Upskilling opportunities</li><li>Hybrid Work Arrangement</li><li>Competitive Remuneration Package</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Who We Looking For</strong></p><p>Our secretaries typically support several lawyers and the role may be challenging and fast paced so you will need to be an efficient worker who is organized, meticulous, self-motivated and resourceful. You will also need to be an excellent communicator, a team player and have integrity to handle highly confidential information appropriately.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Provide efficient secretarial and administrative support to the lawyers in the Corporate practices.</li><li>Maintain lawyer’s clients contact list in the firm’s CRM system.</li><li>Prepare and send out bills including bill narrations.</li><li>Track bills status and send out chasers.</li><li>Prepare legal documents.</li><li>Open new legal files or close files.</li><li>Any other secretarial duties as assigned by supporting lawyers.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Solid secretarial skills and <strong>prior experience in a law firm is preferred</strong>.</li><li>Good proficiency in legal documentation and Microsoft Office applications (in particular, proven experience for Table of Contents in MS Word).</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Attributes</strong></p><ul><li>Meticulous, able to multi-task and work within tight timelines.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We offer a competitive and attractive compensation & benefits package and exciting career development opportunities.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates are invited to apply online with a comprehensive resume, via the <strong>APPLY</strong> button. We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
